Author: Aleph0-4
Text: why do you feel triggered?  is it because you feel like fasting is something you're supposed to be doing and now you feel like you're not as good as your classmate? your classmate will go back to eating normally right after their fast ends but you have unlimited days in the future where you could fast if you want to so you didn't miss any opportunities. 60 kcal is so small, its like you snoozed your fast for 10 minutes
